text: Edward Fanning (16 March 1848 - 30 November 1917) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class cricket match for Victoria in 1873. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1848 births Category:1917 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney Category:Melbourne Cricket Club cricketers
